<br>
I would like to see some actuall numbers on resists, full or partial in skyfire, bewteen a mage in skyfire and a wizard in skyfire.<br>
<br>
I would like the mage to use Scars of sigil and log 50 casts and see how many resists he gets on any mob up in skyfire.  25 casts with no Tishan on it and 25 with.<br>
<br>
I would like the wizard to use drought of fire, because scars is fire based.  I would like him to cast 25 times with no tishan and 25 times with Tishan on it then log down his resists.  Then I would like the wizard to cast drought of Ice on the mobs 25 before 25 after and see the numbers.<br>
<br>
If you post this information please give the level of the mage and wizard, they should be about equal level and each 55+.<br>
<br>
I did this test many months ago with 2 mages in my group.  The numbers I got with Drought of fire were about 40 in 50 resists full or partial, before or after Tishan.  The mages after tishan got off had about 5 in 50 resists with scars of sigil.  With drought of Ice I could not even match these numbers.  I had about 20 in 50 fasts either fully or partially resisted.  I grouped with these 2 mages about 10 times and this happened every time.  There fire spell of scars of sigil was resisted less then my drought of ice after tishan landed.  And with my fire based spell I was so resisted it was not funny.<br>
<br>
If this is true then a mage has a lower inate resist on his spells over a wizard.  And this should be brought up to Verant if it is true for everyone.  <br>
<br>
If you post the information please post the logs also in a row either way so we don't get anyone cheating either way.  People that love the class with post 1 in 50 resists for wizard and people the hate the class will say 45 in 50.  So let's please see logs of the mage and the wizard.<br>
<br>
This is not a rant, but a good learning tool.  If we can back this up and send it verant then maybe they will change our resists to a lesser amount finally. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umyztic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MyztiC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/7/01 8:43:01 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New study</span><hr size=1> Do you mean Tashan-line by Tishan?<br>
